    <item>
      <title>MBK 入股韩国锌业，助其渡过收购纠纷，股价创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/korea-zinc-shares-gain-as-mbk-says-it-secured-substantial-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国锌业公司 (Korea Zinc Co.) 股价上涨至历史新高，此前收购公司 MBK Partners 表示，该公司已收购了足够多的股份，以帮助其赢得对全球最大锌精炼厂的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/korea-zinc-shares-gain-as-mbk-says-it-secured-substantial-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 00:05:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市跟随美国股市上涨；油价下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街再次表现强劲，创下历史新高，亚洲股市随之上涨。随着对以色列袭击伊朗能源设施的担忧缓解，油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 22:26:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
